# Guard against accidentally committing a nested clone of this repo
# (e.g. `git clone` run inside the workspace). A nested copy at
# src/sdk-python/ shadows the real src/strands/ package and makes
# `mypy ./src` fail with a "Duplicate module named 'strands'" error.
/src/sdk-python/
